      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews-patchless/18099/ : SUCCESS\n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/78134/ : SUCCESS",
